records.addlTxt: Order to report to MTPD for photo and prints

BAIL HEARING - 
Defendant in custody and appearing by video from the Manitowoc County Jail.  The State informs the Court that the defendant will be charged with the crime of felony bail jumping and misdemeanor retail theft.  The matter is continued for initial appearance on 03-07-22 at 1:30 p.m.  Bail is set at $1,000.00 recognizance bond with the conditions that he report to the Manitowoc City Police Department for fingerprints, photographs and identifying information within 48 hours or, if incarcerated, within 72 hours of release and defendant is to have no contact with Kelsey Tolman or the Meijer Store in Manitowoc on Rapids Road.  Bail furnished and defendant is released from custody.
